Class TypeDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jpasecurity.jpql.TypeDefinition

  • public class TypeDefinition
extends Object
    This class holds type-definitions of JPQL statements. Types may be defined either in the from-clause or in join-clauses.
